title: Suna
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Colombian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A health food restaurant with a grocery area and a deli area where you can buy sandwiches, soups, and other snacks to takeaway. Uses mostly organic and local ingredients. No fried foods, refined sugar or hydrogenated fats. The menu consists of appetizers, salads, and main entrees predominately plant-based, but there are also chicken and fish. Previously located at Calle 71, 4-47.
